metadata.name: The Pepengers Age Of Ultron
metadata.description: When Pepe Stark tries to jumpstart a dormant peacekeeping program, things go awry and Earth's Mightiest Heroes, including Iron Pepe, Captain Pepe, Thor, Hulk, Black Pepe, and Hawkeye, along with support from Nick Pepe and Maria Pepe are put to the ultimate test as the fate of the planet hangs in the balance.
